Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:58.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba"              "Nanohana"   "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having returned to the\NAlabasta Kingdom at long last,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi and Luffy's party\Nlanded at the port town of Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While hiding from\NBaroque Works' assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the group prepares for a trek across\Nthe desert to stop the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Luffy had rushed\Nahead of everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and found himself\Nlost outside of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Heroes' Reunion!\NHis Name is Fire Fist Ace!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youngster!\NI haven't seen you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time in Alabasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say? Check out\Nthis solid-gold apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is an incredible treasure\NI found in some ancient ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said one bite of this magic gold\Napple will let you live 1000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm not interested\Nin living a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to live today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A solid-gold apple?!\N--1000 years of life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?! For real?! You found\Nit in some ancient ruins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, sure did! It's a legendary\Nartifact of an ancient civilization!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bite and we can live 1000 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! It's the truth! I give you my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have very sharp eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll part with it for\Nthe one-time price of 1000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 Berries?! You got yourself a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't take him seriously if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to live 1000\Nyears for only 1000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit wasting time and look for Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done shopping,\Nso we leave for the next town
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the minute we find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Luffy run off to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a quick question.\NHave you seen this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be here in town. I've been\Nlooking for him for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Never seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if you're looking for someone,\Nask at the restaurant up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner there knows a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant, huh? I was\Njust feeling hungry, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that? He looks incredibly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he looking for Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a former pirate-hunter,\Nthere's no way I wouldn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selling a sword like this for 200,000\NBerries is as good as swindling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have a permit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were\NRoronoa Zoro, and a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rogue like you can't be\Nallowed to own a renowned sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll collect your sword,\Nthe legendary Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that woman doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never try this again!\NDo you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman spells nothing\Nbut trouble! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small fry pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought they could act\Nlike big-shots around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I took care of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in such a distant land, your\Ndistaste for pirates is unfaltering!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got time for pointless chit-chat,\Nhave the royal army take 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be any word yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Straw Hat Luffy having\Ncome to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let your guard down.\NThey will show up. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker? That's the Navy\Ncaptain from Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he followed us\Nall the way here from Loguetown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's that man...\NThings could get ugly quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:08:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thanks for this lunch, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't enough at all one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world is the food place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It seems someone suddenly\Ndied in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He supposedly died in the middle\Nof a conversation with the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think he unwittingly ate a\NDesert Strawberry while traveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Desert Strawberry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're poisonous spiders that\Nlook like red strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat one by accident, and you'll\Nsuddenly keel over a few days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contagious poison spreads through\Nyour corpse a few hours after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so nobody can get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the desert, what you\Ndon't know can kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look! The way he's\Nstill stuck holding the meat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is proof of just how powerful\Nthe Desert Strawberry's poison is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's absurd! You were in the\Nmiddle of a conversation and a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's eating again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this commotion, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this restaurant do\Ncomedy skits or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that.\NBut it's good you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't sleep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, so he wasn't dead after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a false alarm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hit the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this guy been in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pirate who wears a straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're bold\Nenough to eat out in public...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Second Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgas D. Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whitebeard?! The Whitebeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dimwit is one of the\NWhitebeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I have seen\Nthe mark on his back before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mark of\Nthe Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a famous, big-shot\Npirate doing in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! There's a\Nweird smell in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's one! There's a food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To let me capture you quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy trying to find\Nanother pirate at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I have no\Ninterest in taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as I'm a marine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bland reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A food place! I finally found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can eat! I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy! Food! Food! Food!\NOn the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!\NFood! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! This is such a yum food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. Thanks. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, you should probably\Nrun away while you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy that got sent flying\Njust now... Do you know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who sent someone flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did? Who went flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird shop!\NIs this your hobby, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caused it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry for disturbing your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiot would do\Nsomething this crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luf--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did come to Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here, Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you you can't enter\Nthe Grand Line unless you beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Plume-Plume Fruit.\NSo my body becomes smoke at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it? You can't even\Nenter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that smoke!\NWhat're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up! Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran off without paying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! My Gum-Gum moves\Ndon't work on that guy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do for now is run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Captain Smoker?!\NDo you want a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kingdom certainly is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch that guy! It's Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi! Gather the marines at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search every square inch of\Nthis town for Straw Hat's crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People with powers are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat's crew! That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro is in this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Why did you\Ncome to this kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I after? I'm here to\Nbeat up a guy named Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you and Crocodile connected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard thinks he's crafty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Luffy-san have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! He's always such\Na high-maintenance captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we'll be in big trouble\Nif we don't get moving quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a strange man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just find Luffy as quickly\Nas possible and leave town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What for?!\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a big commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him escape! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some idiot pirate must be\Nrunning around town or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that where you guys are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Go get rid of them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Straw Hat crew! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We have to run, obviously!\N--Hurry! To the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Let's get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Yikes! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Haze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be smoke, but I'm fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight between your power\Nand mine would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, anyways?!\NWhy is he helping us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?! Is that you, Ace?!\NYou ate a Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!\NWe're securing the perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, we can't chat like this!\NI'll catch up! You guys run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold these guys off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.\NWhy are you helping Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to\Nworry about his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Brother? You mean to say--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Portgas D. Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's a no-can-do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an acquaintance of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:23:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! This is my brother, Ace! Say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sensible man can't\Npossibly be your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've expected him to\Nbe as reckless as Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy who\Ncares about his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers can be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is just full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace and Luffy!\NHot Emotions and Brotherly Bonds"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
